Partner Transaction
       │
       ▼
Check wallet routing
   ├── Routed to Route A → Route A Module
   │          ├─ Check configured source bank
   │          │   ├─ No active bank → Error / Stuck
   │          │   └─ Bank active → Account Validation
   │          │          ├─ Failed → Stuck
   │          │          └─ Passed → Send Transaction
   │          │                  ├─ Success → Paid
   │          │                  └─ Failure → Processing
   ├── Routed to Route B → Route B Module
   │          ├─ Check configured source bank
   │          │   ├─ No active bank → Error / Stuck
   │          │   └─ Bank active → Account Validation
   │          │          ├─ Failed → Stuck
   │          │          └─ Passed → Send Transaction
   │          │                  ├─ Success → Paid
   │          │                  └─ Failure → Processing
   └── Wallet not routed anywhere → Transaction does not move forward → Stuck
